text.tspan: Craig’s Speed Shop was an in-depth brand exploration class project. The task was to
provide a logo and stationery set for a 1950’s style hot rod mechanic shop. After
finishing the class assignment I decided to explore the brand a little bit further to see
where I could take it. Craig’s is a full-service mechanic steeped in LA race-culture that
specializes in 1950’s hotrod maintenance. After years of owning and operating his
small neighborhood shop, Craig decided he wanted a brand upgrade.
